title: EYL #173 Bounty Killer on Jamaica, Music Business, & Legendary Career

description:
In episode 173 of Earn Your Leisure we spoke with the legendary Bounty Killer. He spoke about his career in music, past issues with Beanie Man, Verzus, Jamaica’s issues, politics, the music business and more. #bountykiller #jamaica #dancehall
